Parking was at the underground parking lot accessible by elevators.	Parking is reasonably priced, secure garage, with in/out privileges... we asked and they let us keep our car in the garage for a couple of extra hours after check out (you should ask though...!	Parking is a bit extra, but your room key allows unlimited in/out, unlike some other hotels in the area.	And the elevator access to/from the parking garage is a bit confusing and inconvenient.	You can park and lock your vehicle in the basement, watch out you have a large SUV or sedan; parking is very tight.